  "title": "Horse Saddle Color Fix",
  "description": "This pack fixes wrong saddle color of horses, mules and donkeys. It changes saddle color brown to orange.",
  "body": "## What is this texture pack?\nThis texture pack fixes wrong horse, mule and donkey saddle color since snapshot 13w18a. When horses were first added, horse saddles were also added, unlike normal saddles. Horse saddles were brown. That's why the saddle texture on the horses was also brown. But horse saddles deleted in snapshot 13w18a. The horse saddle texture color has not been changed since 13w18a.\n## How were looking horse saddles?\nIn 13w16b, horse saddles were like this:\n\n![Horse Saddle From 13w16b](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b8c3fa146d5802b23bc9acdf5ec036750083dab3.png)",
